tweet: Vancouver- Tonight Element57 is hosting an open mic at the Prairie Bar & Grill.  Come down and/or and please tell your musician friends.
Would like to say one more time. What a fantastic time buy real estate in Vancouver, WA. Prices are outstanding...think rental portfolio.
Tomorrow night Element57's song "Ripcord" will be played on Road Rules Challenge- MTV 10p EST.  Hopefully they play a lot of it :)
